0. Install ROS, OpenCV, and boost
1. scientifically surfing the Internet 

2. git clone recursively without SSH key
$ cd catkin_workspace/src
$ git clone --recursive https://github.com/leggedrobotics/darknet_ros.git  
$ cd ../

3. $ catkin_make -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release

4. test 
$ catkin build darknet_ros --no-deps --verbose --catkin-make-args run_tests

5. get pretrained weights
$ wget http://pjreddie.com/media/files/yolov3.weights
$ wget http://pjreddie.com/media/files/yolo9000.weights


6. # make gpu version darknet according to InstallGPUVersionDarknet





